# 4. Add business logs in stub-server

## In `/post-login`

Log:

* code received
* Arthur exchange start
* Arthur exchange success
* local session/security context created
* redirect to `/B2BOOST`

```java
log.info("Received /post-login with code={}", code);
log.info("Calling Arthur Core handoff exchange");
log.info("Handoff exchange succeeded for userId={}, username={}", login.getUserId(), login.getUsername());
log.info("Security context created for username={}", login.getUsername());
log.info("Redirecting to {}", request.getContextPath() + "/B2BOOST");
```

## In homepage controller

Log authenticated principal:

```java
log.info("Accessing B2BOOST with principal={}", authentication.getName());
```

