# 8. Add SecurityContext logger in stub-server

To prove login worked there.

```java
@Component
@Slf4j
public class SecurityContextLoggingFilter extends OncePerRequestFilter {

    @Override
    protected void doFilterInternal(
            HttpServletRequest request,
            HttpServletResponse response,
            FilterChain filterChain
    ) throws ServletException, IOException {

        Authentication auth = SecurityContextHolder.getContext().getAuthentication();

        if (auth != null) {
            log.info("SecurityContext authentication name={}, authorities={}",
                    auth.getName(), auth.getAuthorities());
        } else {
            log.info("SecurityContext is empty");
        }

        filterChain.doFilter(request, response);
    }
}
```

This is most useful in **stub-server**.

