# 9. Use MDC in log pattern

In `application.yml` for all apps:

```yaml
logging:
  pattern:
    console: "%d{yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS} [%thread] %-5level %logger{36} [flowId=%X{flowId}] - %msg%n"
```

Then every log line shows:

```text
[flowId=abc-123]
```

That makes the whole login chain readable.

