# 10. Good logger levels by app

## Arthur Core

Use:

* your package: `DEBUG`
* Spring Security: `DEBUG`
* WebClient/reactor: `DEBUG`

```yaml
logging:
  level:
    com.yourcompany.arthurcore: DEBUG
    org.springframework.security: DEBUG
    org.springframework.web.reactive.function.client: DEBUG
    reactor.netty.http.client: DEBUG
```

## Lancelot

Use:

* your package: `DEBUG`
* Spring web/jpa if needed

```yaml
logging:
  level:
    com.yourcompany.lancelot: DEBUG
    org.springframework.web: INFO
    org.hibernate.SQL: DEBUG
```

If you want SQL params too:

```yaml
logging:
  level:
    org.hibernate.orm.jdbc.bind: TRACE
```

## stub-server

Use:

* your package: `DEBUG`
* Spring Security: `DEBUG`
* WebClient/reactor: `DEBUG`

```yaml
logging:
  level:
    com.yourcompany.stubserver: DEBUG
    org.springframework.security: DEBUG
    org.springframework.web.reactive.function.client: DEBUG
    reactor.netty.http.client: DEBUG
```

