# 12. Smallest useful set to add first

If you want the fastest path, add just these:

## Arthur Core

* logs in `/auth/start`
* logs in `/auth/callback`
* logs in `/auth/handoff/exchange`

## Lancelot

* logs in `getApp`
* logs in `getUserById`

## stub-server

* logs in `/post-login`
* logs in homepage
* `org.springframework.security=DEBUG`

That alone will make the full flow readable.

